---
/**
 * API key request path. Sources: cadence.core.middleware.authentication.AuthenticationMiddleware,
 * tenant context middleware building ApiKeyTokenSession from request.state.api_key_row.
 */
---

<div class="diagram-wrap">
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    viewBox="0 0 420 200"
    role="img"
    aria-labelledby="ak-title ak-desc"
    class="diagram-svg"
  >
    <title id="ak-title">API key authentication flow</title>
    <desc id="ak-desc">
      X-API-KEY header is validated in AuthenticationMiddleware, then TenantContextMiddleware builds
      a synthetic session.
    </desc>
    <rect
      x="12"
      y="12"
      width="396"
      height="36"
      rx="6"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.08"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="1"></rect>
    <text
      x="210"
      y="36"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="12"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
    >
      HTTP request with
      <tspan font-weight="600">X-API-KEY</tspan>
      header
    </text>
    <line x1="210" y1="48" x2="210" y2="64" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"></line>
    <rect
      x="40"
      y="68"
      width="340"
      height="44"
      rx="5"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.06"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="1"></rect>
    <text
      x="210"
      y="90"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="11"
      font-weight="600"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
    >
      AuthenticationMiddleware
    </text>
    <text
      x="210"
      y="106"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="10"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.85"
    >
      Hash lookup → request.state.api_key_row
    </text>
    <line x1="210" y1="112" x2="210" y2="128" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"></line>
    <rect
      x="40"
      y="132"
      width="340"
      height="52"
      rx="5"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.06"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="1"></rect>
    <text
      x="210"
      y="156"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="11"
      font-weight="600"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
    >
      TenantContextMiddleware
    </text>
    <text
      x="210"
      y="172"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="10"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.85"
    >
      ApiKeyTokenSession + memberships; scopes via sanitize_api_key_flat_scopes
    </text>
  </svg>
  <p class="diagram-caption">
    See <a href="/concepts/security-and-access/">Security and access</a> for JWT versus API key paths
    and{' '}
    <code>cadence.core.middleware_setup</code> registration order in <code>cadence.main</code>.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  @layer starlight.components {
    .diagram-wrap {
      color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
      margin: 0.75rem 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .diagram-svg {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 30rem;
      height: auto;
    }

    .diagram-caption {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
      font-size: var(--sl-text-sm);
      color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
      max-width: 34rem;
    }

    .diagram-caption code {
      font-size: 0.92em;
    }
  }
</style>
